	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Lightning</h1>
	
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
		<div id="contentSub"></div>
		
		
		<div id="jump-to-nav"></div>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="Lightning#mw-head">Jump to navigation</a>
		<a class="mw-jump-link" href="Lightning#p-search">Jump to search</a>
		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">For other uses, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lightning_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Lightning (disambiguation)">Lightning (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">"Return stroke" redirects here. For other uses, see <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Return_stroke_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Return stroke (disambiguation)">Return stroke (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable">Not to be confused with <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lighting" title="Lighting">Lighting</a>.</div>
<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Weather phenomenon involving electrostatic discharge</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
