<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none;padding:0"><div class="NavHead" style="font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left"><b>Glossaries</b></div><div class="NavContent" style="font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center">
<ul><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Glossary_of_meteorology" title="Glossary of meteorology">Meteorology</a></li>
