<li id="cite_note-121"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Lightning#cite_ref-121">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://infoniac.com/science/terawatt-laser-beam-shot-clouds-provokes-lightning-strike.html">"Terawatt Laser Beam Shot in the Clouds Provokes Lightning Strike"</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20080420130439/http://infoniac.com/science/terawatt-laser-beam-shot-clouds-provokes-lightning-strike.html">Archived</a> from the original on April 20, 2008.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Terawatt+Laser+Beam+Shot+in+the+Clouds+Provokes+Lightning+Strike&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Finfoniac.com%2Fscience%2Fterawatt-laser-beam-shot-clouds-provokes-lightning-strike.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALightning" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/> News report based on: <cite id="CITEREFKasparianAckermannAndréMéchain2008" class="citation journal">Kasparian, J.; Ackermann, R.; André, Y. B.; Méchain, G. G.; Méjean, G.; Prade, B.; Rohwetter, P.; Salmon, E.; Stelmaszczyk, K.; Yu, J.; Mysyrowicz, A.; Sauerbrey, R.; Woeste, L.; Wolf, J. P. (2008). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive-ouverte.unige.ch/unige:37869">"Electric events synchronized with laser filaments in thunderclouds"</a>. <i>Optics Express</i>. <b>16</b> (8): 5757–63. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bibcode_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Bibcode (identifier)">Bibcode</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2008OExpr..16.5757K">2008OExpr..16.5757K</a>. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1364%2FOE.16.005757">10.1364/OE.16.005757</a>. <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PMID_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="PMID (identifier)">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18542684">18542684</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Optics+Express&amp;rft.atitle=Electric+events+synchronized+with+laser+filaments+in+thunderclouds&amp;rft.volume=16&amp;rft.issue=8&amp;rft.pages=5757-63&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F18542684&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1364%2FOE.16.005757&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F2008OExpr..16.5757K&amp;rft.aulast=Kasparian&amp;rft.aufirst=J.&amp;rft.au=Ackermann%2C+R.&amp;rft.au=Andr%C3%A9%2C+Y.+B.&amp;rft.au=M%C3%A9chain%2C+G.+G.&amp;rft.au=M%C3%A9jean%2C+G.&amp;rft.au=Prade%2C+B.&amp;rft.au=Rohwetter%2C+P.&amp;rft.au=Salmon%2C+E.&amp;rft.au=Stelmaszczyk%2C+K.&amp;rft.au=Yu%2C+J.&amp;rft.au=Mysyrowicz%2C+A.&amp;rft.au=Sauerbrey%2C+R.&amp;rft.au=Woeste%2C+L.&amp;rft.au=Wolf%2C+J.+P.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive-ouverte.unige.ch%2Funige%3A37869&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALightning" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/><sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span style="white-space: nowrap;">&#91;<i><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Link_rot" title="Wikipedia:Link rot"><span title="&#160;Dead link since September 2019">permanent dead link</span></a></i>&#93;</span></sup></span>
